-- Alliance Data Systems profit rises 18 pct
-- 
-- Thu Jul 17, 2014 07:41AM EDT
-- None



July 17 (Reuters) - Credit card processor Alliance Data Systems Corp <ADS.N> reported an 18 percent rise in quarterly profit, helped by strong sales in its customer loyalty programs business.

The company's net income attributable to shareholders rose to $137.4 million, or $2.19 per share, in the quarter ended June 30, from $116.4 million, or $1.71 per share, a year earlier. [ID:nPn9C9gRz]